    ++++Understand page elements<br/>
    Dropmenu: Dropmenus are the main navigational menu that provides all sorts of dropdown items. Inorder to change the content of the navigational link, you must change it by hard coding. 
    Banners: these banners are 8*2 or 7*2 in ratio. their width is 891px, height is 250px. Anything that is heigher than 25px will get removed.<br />
	Header Text: header text is a type of text that is being displayed right under the banner. usually in bold. ONLY ONE HEADER TEXT PER PAGE PLEASE.<br />
    Page Entrees: you can have many page entrees per page. they are your regular posts governed by a second tier page category and a third tier page tag.<br />
	Square Links: Square links are the little square elements on the left side under all the page entrees. these are designed for fancy quick navigation into other pages.<br />
    Right Side Links: Right side links happen only on third page tiers. they are side links that are meant for quick navigational purposes. <br />
    Foot: footer is the bottom image. it has no functionality. <br />  <br />
  
    
    
    ++++Understanding managers<br />
	Post Managers: this manager is your bread and butter. it can upload any kind of page elment on to any page, except for the special pages described in the page tier section. <br />
	Product Manager: this manager only governs the TEAM APPERREL <br />
	Registration Manager: this manager only governs the Become a member now!!!<br />
    Media managers: photo manager is currently not working, to upload pictures please see the upload picture section. Video manager is open for all<br /> 
    Order managers: order managers manages all the orders that came through the website such as registration payment or apparel purchases.<br />
	Help manager: that is this. <br /><br />

    
    ++++Understanding wysiwyg editor<br />
	WYSIWYG: this is the EDITOR that allows you to make all your post edits. This is a VERY VERY POWERFULL tool. It allows you to style your posts, help you add inline LINKS, inline IMAGES, inline youtube VIDEO POPUPS, inline GOOGLE CALENDER, MAPS, AND ANYTHING YOU WANT! This is the tool that makes everything happen. Embrace it and love it! For more detailed description on how to use this, you may visit the WYSIWYG details below. <br /><br />
    
