	------------------------------------------Upload a banner------------------------------------------<br />
    Management Type: Post manager<br />
    Existing: Banners can exist in tier. <br />
    Title Link: the location on where you want the banner to link to after clicking on it.
    Display: Your post image is only being displayed.<br />
    Function: If there is more than one image in your banner post, the banner will cycle through the banners at every 8 seconds. <br />
    Category: ****Banners****<br />
